2011-08-25 v1.0.0
-----------------

* Added the ability to filter / bind condition values at the last minute for
  conditions. Simply provide a prefix and a callable in getConditionFilters;
  see AdvancedReport::getConditionFilters() for an example.
* Moved the settings of the report to a separate tab

2011-04-05 v0.1.2
-----------------

* Fixed problem where empty values were not being passed through to formatting functions
* Fixed formatting of table in PDF
* Allow PDF previews

2011-03-28 v0.1.1
-----------------

* Ability to specific IS NOT NULL and IS NULL conditions

2011-02-15 v0.1.0
-----------------

* First release
